=== Hyogo Prefecture === * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Taishi)|ja|崇導神社 (揖保郡太子町)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Taishi, Ibo County; Main deity: Prince Toneri * {{ill|Sudō Tennō Jinja (Tatsuno)|ja|崇道天皇神社 (たつの市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Tatsuno City * {{ill|Sōdō Jinja|ja|総道神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – Shisō City; Main deity: {{ill|Sarutahiko|ja|猿田彦神|12=draft|12=draft}}
=== Okayama Prefecture === * {{ill|Sōdō Jinja (Tsuyama)|ja|宗道神社 (津山市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Tsuyama City<ref>{{Cite web|title=ありし日の鍛冶職人の心意気を伝える宗道神社|url=https://afw-at.com/page.php?id=100|accessdate=2019-03-08}}</ref> * {{ill|Kamo Jinja|ja|加茂神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – Tsuyama City (formerly Sugi Daimyōjin-sha, renamed due to nearby tomb) * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Ibara)|ja|崇道神社 (井原市)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Ibara City * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Yakage)|ja|崇道神社 (小田郡矢掛町)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Yakage, Oda County
=== Hiroshima Prefecture === * {{ill|Sōdo Jinja|ja|惣戸神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – Fukuyama City * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Fukuyama)|ja|崇堂神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – Fukuyama City; Main deity: Oka Shimamori Kagekatsu * {{ill|Sōdō Myōjin-sha|ja|惣堂明神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – Fukuyama City; Main deity: {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|足利義昭|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Kami-Sōdō Jinja|ja|上惣堂神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – Fukuyama City; Main deity: Ashikaga Yoshiaki * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Jinseki)|ja|崇道神社 (神石郡神石高原町)|12=draft|12=draft}} – Jinseki-Kōgen, Jinseki County
