=== Kyoto Prefecture === * {{ill|Sudō Jinja|ja|崇道神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja|qq=}} – Kamitakano, Sakyō-ku, Kyoto City
=== Nara Prefecture === * {{ill|Sudō Tennō-sha (abolished)|ja|八島陵#崇道天皇社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Tennō-sha (abolished)|qq=}} – Formerly atop Yashima Tomb; now merged with {{ill|Shimada Jinja|ja|嶋田神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimada Jinja|qq=}} * {{ill|Sudō Tennō-sha|ja|崇道天皇社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Tennō-sha|qq=}} – Nishikidera-cho, Nara City * {{ill|Sudō Tennō Jinja (Deyashiki)|ja|八島陵#出屋敷町 崇道天皇神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Tennō Jinja (Deyashiki)|qq=}} – Deyashiki-cho, Nara City * {{ill|Sudō Tennō Jinja (Kodono)|ja|八島陵#神殿町 崇道天皇神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Tennō Jinja (Kodono)|qq=}} – Kodono-cho, Nara City * {{ill|Sudō Tennō Jinja (Kitanagai)|ja|八島陵#北永井町 崇道天皇神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Tennō Jinja (Kitanagai)|qq=}} – Kitanagai-cho, Nara City * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Gose)|ja|崇道神社 (御所市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja (Gose)|qq=}} – Gose City
=== Hyōgo Prefecture === * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Taishi)|ja|崇導神社 (揖保郡太子町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja (Taishi)|qq=}} – Taishi, Ibo County; Main deity: Prince Toneri * {{ill|Sudō Tennō Jinja (Tatsuno)|ja|崇道天皇神社 (たつの市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Tennō Jinja (Tatsuno)|qq=}} – Tatsuno City * {{ill|Sōdō Jinja|ja|総道神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sōdō Jinja|qq=}} – Shisō City; Main deity: {{ill|Sarutahiko|ja|猿田彦神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sarutahiko|qq=}}
=== Okayama Prefecture === * {{ill|Sōdō Jinja (Tsuyama)|ja|宗道神社 (津山市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sōdō Jinja (Tsuyama)|qq=}} – Tsuyama City<ref>{{Cite web|title=ありし日の鍛冶職人の心意気を伝える宗道神社|url=https://afw-at.com/page.php?id=100|accessdate=2019-03-08}}</ref> * {{ill|Kamo Jinja|ja|加茂神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamo Jinja|qq=}} – Tsuyama City (formerly Sugi Daimyōjin-sha, renamed due to nearby tomb) * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Ibara)|ja|崇道神社 (井原市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja (Ibara)|qq=}} – Ibara City * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Yakage)|ja|崇道神社 (小田郡矢掛町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja (Yakage)|qq=}} – Yakage, Oda County
=== Hiroshima Prefecture === * {{ill|Sōdo Jinja|ja|惣戸神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sōdo Jinja|qq=}} – Fukuyama City * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Fukuyama)|ja|崇堂神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja (Fukuyama)|qq=}} – Fukuyama City; Main deity: Oka Shimamori Kagekatsu * {{ill|Sōdō Myōjin-sha|ja|惣堂明神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sōdō Myōjin-sha|qq=}} – Fukuyama City; Main deity: {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|足利義昭|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=}} * {{ill|Kami-Sōdō Jinja|ja|上惣堂神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kami-Sōdō Jinja|qq=}} – Fukuyama City; Main deity: Ashikaga Yoshiaki * {{ill|Sudō Jinja (Jinseki)|ja|崇道神社 (神石郡神石高原町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sudō Jinja (Jinseki)|qq=}} – Jinseki-Kōgen, Jinseki County
